						<summary>

						<p>Inscribed fragment (No. 1) from a field near the palace area of excavation site No. 7.</p>						

						<p>Undated. Palaeographically attributable to the Brāhmī of 3rd century A.D. Written in the Prākṛit language.</p>						

						<p>Seems to refer to the gift of a pillar.</p>						

